---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import BackToTop from '../components/BackToTop.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="About Me" description="About this blog and its author" />
		<meta name="base-url" content={import.meta.env.BASE_URL} />
	</head>

	<body>
		<a href="#main-content" class="skip-link">Skip to main content</a>
		<Header />
		
		<main id="main-content" class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-4xl min-h-screen">
			<figure class="mb-8">
				<img src={AboutHeroImage.src} alt="About" class="rounded-xl w-full max-h-96 object-cover" />
			</figure>
			
			<div class="mb-6">
				<h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">About Me</h1>
				<div class="divider"></div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
				<p class="text-lg text-base-content/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
					I often researching about something in AI. As I used multiple AI, I need to save them in one place. Also, I don't want to mix my own thoughts and researches with AI generated contents. It's confusing for me and anybody else.
				</p>
				<p class="text-lg text-base-content/80 leading-relaxed">
					For these reasons, I think best to gather all of the researches on this blog.
				</p>
				
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">About This Blog</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-base-content/80 leading-relaxed">
					This blog serves as a repository for AI-generated research and analysis on various topics. The content here is primarily created with the assistance of artificial intelligence tools, exploring subjects ranging from technology and digital systems to economics and global affairs.
				</p>
				
				<div class="alert mt-8">
					<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="stroke-info shrink-0 w-6 h-6">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
					</svg>
					<div>
						<h3 class="font-bold">Notice</h3>
						<div class="text-sm">
							Content on this site is mostly generated by AI. <span class="text-warning font-medium">Viewer discretion is advised.</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>
		
		<BackToTop />
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
